For running python program with arguments of attack destination, 
in terminal,
	key in "python attack.py 'ip of destination'" 
	or
	"chmod +x attack.py"
	"./attack.py 'ip of destination'"


For running python program,
in terminal,
	key in "python atack.py"
	or
	"chmod +x attack.py"
	"./attack.py"

TO CHANGE THE PING COMMAND
open attack.py with gedit,
	goto line 14, mess around with it.

TO CHECK THE PROCESS
in terminal,
	key in "top"

TO STOP THE PROGRAM
in terminal,
	key in "killall ping"
*the program doesn't come with terminate commands, so the process have to be kill manually
